## Key Differences: Baseline vs Advanced

| Feature | Baseline (`train_baseline.py`) | Advanced (`train_v4_robust.py`) |
|---|---|---|
| Backbone | **Frozen** (0 trainable base layers) | Unfrozen last 100 layers |
| Ensemble | Single model, seed 42 | 5-seed ensemble (42–46) |
| SWA | ❌ | ✅ Last 5 epochs |
| TTA | ❌ | ✅ Multi-scale + flip |
| Mixup | ❌ | ✅ Alpha=0.1 |
| Label Smoothing | ❌ (0.0) | ✅ (0.05) |
| LR Schedule | Fixed 1e-4 | Cosine Decay |
| Hard Example Oversampling | ❌ | ✅ 20–30× |
| Color Jitter | ❌ | ✅ Hue + saturation |
| Dropout | ❌ | ✅ 0.4 |
| L2 Regularization | ❌ | ✅ 0.0002 |
| Grad-CAM | Standard | Eigen + Aug Smooth |
| Callbacks | Checkpoint + EarlyStopping | Checkpoint + Cosine LR + SWA |

